
Required perl modules (only top level dependencies are listed)

Email::Folder
Email::Thread
Email::Mime
CGI (distributed with perl 5.10.0; maybe before?)

You also need a very new version of ikiwiki: post 2.62.1, with the following 
patch or equivalant applied:

From 84f40d7fa822c6cc09506cca2dbf38a8b19f8bb7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: David Bremner <bremner@unb.ca>
Date: Fri, 29 Aug 2008 20:46:20 -0300
Subject: [PATCH] call File::MimeInfo::default if ::magic() returns undef

